{"tid":508550,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"新垣結衣（236）「Merry Christmas」","createTime":"2017-12-24T11:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T08:17:59.000Z","uid":25382,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"137dc12ee889a7c32551421ef2e3cbbab4c1d257","tid":508550,"uid":25382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:11:13.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rC72OXT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrC72OXT.png&h=8b3c0232&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-新post格式：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/1jRJUk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F1jRJUk&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a56b478e\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/1jRJUk</a><br />\n- <strong>2樓入門攻略、投票區、綜藝<br />\n廣告、相集、Google drive綜合下載</strong><br />\n- 3樓新劇/電影資訊<br />\n<br />\n-頭post出齊先好留名 記得正皮<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Ul7S4Mn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUl7S4Mn.gif&h=c75e1702&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/v8rgmyt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fv8rgmyt.png&h=49d0d8d3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>標題來源：</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/xULW8jqq2jVyn1fLmU/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FxULW8jqq2jVyn1fLmU%2Fgiphy.gif&h=019336de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>2018掛曆/枱曆</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7jfYPvL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7jfYPvL.jpg&h=e0b37c78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周邊產品攻略：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/CtQfX9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FCtQfX9&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=4553f7bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/CtQfX9</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BT0s9K7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBT0s9K7.png&h=babee597&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>結衣畫畫活動</strong></span></span><br />\n自己揀一個場面黎畫（唔一定畫結衣）<br />\n畫風、畫畫工具不限 題材跟結衣出演既作品 每期轉一套<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今期係<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">S 最後的警官</span></strong></span><br />\n每10個post就會一次過po作品<br />\n今期畫作會出係post <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">236</span></strong>  <br />\n已完成畫作可以Email比那年巴<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Email：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n附上作品時唔該俾埋Lihkg User Name同ID<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">另外建議大家影自己作品個時可以用App: Office Lens/CamScanner去影<br />\n會有Scan嘅效果,不過並非硬性規定一定要用</span></div>"},{"pid":"6f2c15b51cfcd5bffa6e7f9272e8c2228fe73386","tid":508550,"uid":25382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:11:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>新手上路主線攻略</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/TnYOcs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FTnYOcs&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=2c0a3265\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/TnYOcs</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">日劇冷知識：</span></strong><br />\n日本無分男 / 女主角呢樣野<br />\n得一個主演，好少會有雙主演<br />\n例如結衣係主演，星野源就要係助演<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>周邊產品攻略</span><br />\n(官方月曆、CD、代言產品等等)</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/CtQfX9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FCtQfX9&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=4553f7bc\" target=\"