/span><br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/qXk2TG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FqXk2TG&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=9473e14e\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/qXk2TG</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/g2p80f3xn/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2Fg2p80f3xn%2Fimage.jpg&h=de5a979b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s2.postimg.org/ezlnk1wk9/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs2.postimg.org%2Fezlnk1wk9%2Fimage.jpg&h=9bd77732&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>巴絲打區：</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n重點連結：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/yvoJwK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FyvoJwK&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=d7975aea\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/yvoJwK</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/BQxA8i5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBQxA8i5.gif&h=fd7485c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCredit：華田"},{"pid":"765a65cebb8ceacfc887c69dcc8bc2914890a251","tid":508550,"uid":25382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:11:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">《Code Blue 3》電影版製作決定！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/O1bGuox.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FO1bGuox.gif&h=e9026d1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官網：<a href=\"http://www.fujitv.co.jp/codeblue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fujitv.co.jp%2Fcodeblue%2F&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=b698bd4f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fujitv.co.jp/codeblue/</a><br />\nTwitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/code_blue2017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcode_blue2017&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=495196dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/code_blue2017</a><br />\n預告：待補<br />\n上映時間：2018年7月27日(日本)<br />\n<br />\n出演：<br />\n山下智久、新垣結衣、戶田惠梨香、比嘉愛未<br />\n淺利陽介、有岡大貴、成田凌、新木優子<br />\n馬場富美加、安藤政信、椎名桔平<br />\nSTAFF：<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/khHqBVo.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkhHqBVo.png&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=3e055768\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/khHqBVo.png</a><br />\n<br />\n主題曲 - Mr.Children - HANABI<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VZ1q8VlF8Ao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVZ1q8VlF8Ao&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=0716861f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VZ1q8VlF8Ao</a><br />\n<br />\n　　時間設定於第2季的七年後，藍澤耕作（山下智久飾）離開了翔陽大學附屬北部醫院的急救中心，成為了一名神經外科醫生。白石惠<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">（新垣結衣飾）</span></strong>依然在人手不足的急救中心擔當著領導者的角色。曾經也夢想成為飛行急救醫生的緋山美帆子（戶田惠梨香飾）離開翔陽醫院，成為了婦產科醫生。冴島遙（比嘉愛未飾）依然從事著飛行急救護士的工作。藤川一男 （淺利陽介飾）與白石一起留在急救中心，成為了一名整形的急救醫生。<br />\n<br />\n關係圖：<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DBrncZZUQAAKdmC.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDBrncZZUQAAKdmC.jpg&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=285ce5e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DBrncZZUQAAKdmC.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\ncb3官網新垣結衣採訪部分：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/6ovdUm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F6ovdUm&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=5fe268bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/6ovdUm</a>"},{"pid":"f01d45ce4b07c4829eb3b6d933389334e53137c7","tid":508550,"uid":62635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:12:01.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"7c3927cab24443feef7c9f036f853b20721382b1","tid":508550,"uid":51944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:12:02.000Z","msg":"做乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src